      "content": "it's more than just a \"system\" or a \"dynamic.\" it feels more like a glitch. no matter how much I change, the outcome is always the same. i feel like i've tried every possible way to fix it and i'm still right back here at the start. it feels like there's no way out of the cycle except to just... stop.",
